ed="T" n="0761c16"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0761c16"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000009186">潤州幽棲寺</placeName><persName key="A010251">玄素</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0761c17"/><persName key="A010251">釋玄素</persName>，字<persName key="A010251">道清</persName>，俗緣馬氏，<placeName key="PL000000011063">潤州延陵</placeName>人也。生<lb
ed="T" n="0761c18"/>有異度，幼而深仁，乳育安靜。髫齓<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g280"/>希<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1451"/>尚，求<lb
ed="T" n="0761c19"/>歸釋門，父母從之，出依淨域。以<date notBefore-iso="+0692-04-25" key="j19739231974106" notAfter-iso="+0692-10-25">如意年中</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0761c20"/>始奉制度，隷名于<placeName key="PL000000008801">江寧長壽寺</placeName>。進具已後，戒<lb
ed="T" n="0761c21"/>光騰燭，定水澄漣，思入玄微<ptr type="glossary" target="#g773"/>，行逾人表。既<lb
ed="T" n="0761c22"/>解色空，常慕宗匠。晚年乃南入<placeName key="PL000000009186">青山幽棲<lb
ed="T" n="0761c23"/>寺</placeName><ptr target="#n1394"/>，因事<persName key="A010051">威<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，躬歷彌載，撞鐘大鳴。<persName key="A010051">威</persName>誨<lb
ed="T" n="0761c24"/>以勝法，得其不刊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g690"/>之旨。從是伏形苦節，交<lb
ed="T" n="0761c25"/>養恬和，敗納<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1322"/><anchor xml:id="beg0761005"/>襯<anchor xml:id="end0761005"/>身，寒暑不易，貴賤怨親，曾<lb
ed="T" n="0761c26"/>無喜慍，時目之為嬰兒行<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1452"/>菩薩。道業既高，<lb
ed="T" n="0761c27"/><anchor xml:id="beg0761006"/>人<anchor xml:id="end0761006"/>希瞻<anchor xml:id="beg0761sgsz4"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0761sgsz4"/>。<date notBefore-iso="+0713-12-26" key="j19818371992113" notAfter-iso="+0742-02-13">開元年中</date>，僧<persName key="A010252"><anchor xml:id="beg0761sgsz5"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>汪</sic><corr>法</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0761sgsz5"/>密</persName>請至<placeName key="PL000000010985">京口</placeName><ptr target="#n1395"/>，郡<lb
ed="T" n="0761c28"/>牧<persName key="A010253">韋銑</persName>屈居<placeName key="PL000000011009">鶴林</placeName>，四部<ptr type="glossary" target="#g98"/>歸誠，充塞寺宇。<persName key="A010251">素</persName>納<lb
ed="T" n="0761c29"/>衣空床，未甞出戶，王侯稽首，不為動搖。顧世<pb ed="T" n="0762a" xml:id="T50.2061.0762a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0762a01"/>名利，猶如幻焉。忽於一日，有屠者來<anchor xml:id="beg0762sgsz1"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0762sgsz1"/>謁，<lb
ed="T" n="0762a02"/>自生感悟，懺悔先罪，求請<persName key="A010251">素</persName>明中應供，乃<lb
ed="T" n="0762a03"/>欣然受之，降詣其舍。士庶驚駭，咸稱「異哉」。<lb
ed="T" n="0762a04"/><persName key="A010251">素</persName>曰：「佛性是同，無生<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1368"/>豈別？但可度者，<ref type="person" target="#A010251">吾</ref>其度<lb
ed="T" n="0762a05"/>之，何異之有？」<date notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14" key="j19921141993438" notAfter-iso="+0745-09-30"><name>天寶</name>之初</date>，<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000013239">越</placeName>瞻仰如想下<lb
ed="T" n="0762a06"/>生<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1457"/>。<placeName key="PL000000010783">楊州</placeName>僧<persName key="A010254">希玄</persName>請至<placeName key="PL000000000093">江北</placeName><ptr target="#n1400"/>，竊而宵遁。黑月難<lb
ed="T" n="0762a07"/>濟，江波淼然，持舟擬風。俄頃有白光一道，<lb
ed="T" n="0762a08"/>引棹直渡，通波獲全。<placeName key="PL000000010514">楚</placeName>人相慶佛日再耀。<lb
ed="T" n="0762a09"/>傾州奔赴，會於津所。人物拒道，間無立位，<lb
ed="T" n="0762a10"/>解衣投施，積若山丘。略不干其懷抱，令悉<lb
ed="T" n="0762a11"/>充悲田<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1453"/>之費。禮部尚書<persName key="A010255">李憕</persName>為<placeName key="PL000000010783">楊州</placeName>牧，齋心<lb
ed="T" n="0762a12"/>虔虔，二時<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1114"/>瞻近。未幾而<placeName key="PL000000010985">京口</placeName>道俗思渴法音，<lb
ed="T" n="0762a13"/>仍移牒渡<placeName key="PL000000000150">江</placeName>，再請還<ref type="place" target="#PL000000010783">郡</ref>。二處紛諍，莫決所<lb
ed="T" n="0762a14"/>從。<persName key="A010255">李</persName>時謂人曰：「本期奉道，反成愛憎。」因任<lb
ed="T" n="0762a15"/>從所請，却歸<ref type="place" target="#PL000000010783">南郡</ref>，其感物慕德，罕有與倫。<lb
ed="T" n="0762a16"/>以<date key="j19960811996081" when-iso="+0752-12-25"><name>天寶</name>十一載十一月十一日</date>中夜，無疾而<lb
ed="T" n="0762a17"/>化，春秋八十有五<ptr target="#n376"/>。哀感人倫，慟徹城市。以<lb
ed="T" n="0762a18"/><date key="j19960911996091" when-iso="+0753-01-04">其月二十一日</date>奉全身建塔于<placeName key="PL000000011008">黃鶴山</placeName>西所住<lb
ed="T" n="0762a19"/>之地。方伯<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1454"/>、邑宰<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1455"/>盡執喪師之禮，率眾申哀，<lb
ed="T" n="0762a20"/>江湖震響。<persName key="A010251">素</persName>往於寺內坐禪之所，高松偃覆<lb
ed="T" n="0762a21"/>如蓋，及移他樹，還互如前。又當捨壽之<lb
ed="T" n="0762a22"/>夕，房前雙桐無故自枯。識者以為<placeName key="PL000000048391">雙林</placeName>之變。<lb
ed="T" n="0762a23"/>但真乘妙理，絕相難思；嘉瑞靈祥，應感必有。<lb
ed="T" n="0762a24"/>《經》云：「隨緣赴感」<ptr target="#n1396"/>，即其事也。有門弟子<persName key="A010257">法鑑</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0762a25"/>及<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳中</placeName><persName key="A004218">法欽</persName>，此二大士重光道原，僉具別<lb
ed="T" n="0762a26"/>傳。受菩薩戒弟子吏部侍郎<persName key="A010258">齊澣</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000030464">廣州</placeName>都督<lb
ed="T" n="0762a27"/><persName key="A019134">粱<supplied>昇</supplied>卿</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000010986">潤州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A010260">徐嶠</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000042192">京兆</placeName><persName key="A010261">韋昭理</persName>、給事中<persName key="A010262">韓賞</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0762a28"/>御史中丞<persName key="A010263">李<anchor xml:id="beg0762sgsz2"/>丹<anchor xml:id="end0762sgsz2"/></persName>、禮部<persName key="A010264">崔令欽</persName>，並道流人望，咸<lb
ed="T" n="0762a29"/>欵師資，亦甞問道於<persName key="A004218">徑山</persName>，猶<persName key="A019135">樂正子春</persName>於<pb ed="T" n="0762b" xml:id="T50.2061.0762b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0762b01"/><ref type="person" target="#A002174">夫子</ref><ptr target="#n1397"/>。洗心瞻仰，天漢<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1456"/>彌高；水鑑明心，悟深者<lb
ed="T" n="0762b02"/>眾矣。洎<date notBefore-iso="+0827-03-18" key="j20231922026427" notAfter-iso="+0836-01-25"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0762001"/>太<anchor xml:id="end0762001"/>和</name>中</date>，遠慕遺風，高其令德，追<lb
ed="T" n="0762b03"/>諡<persName key="A010251">大律<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，<placeName key="PL000000056377"><anchor xml:id="beg0762sgsz3"/>太<anchor xml:id="end0762sgsz3"/>和大寶杭之塔</placeName><ptr target="#n1398"/>。後人多以<lb
ed="T" n="0762b04"/>俗氏召之曰<persName key="A010251">馬祖</persName>，或以姓名兼稱曰<persName key="A010251">馬素</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0762b05"/>是也。</p>
    <p><lb
ed="T" n="0762b06"/>系曰：<persName key="A001503">彌天</persName>以出家子咸姓釋氏，懸合後到<lb
ed="T" n="0762b07"/>《阿含經》<ptr target="#n1399"/>，可不務乎？<persName key="A010251">素<roleName>師</roleName></persName>以俗姓呼之，必有<lb
ed="T" n="0762b08"/>由矣。噫，繁盛法嗣，猶不能遏此訛稱，則知<lb
ed="T" n="0762b09"/><persName key="A010251">素<roleName>師</roleName></persName>名翼一飛，四海仰止，故登俗域。今警將<lb
ed="T" n="0762b10"/>來，宜正名也。</p>
